Mangala joined Porto in 2011 from Belgium club Standard Liege and has made 92 appearances in total.

He made his international debut last month in France's 1-0 friendly defeat to Uruguay and was part of Didier Deschamps' squad for the World Cup in Brazil although he did not feature. 

